name: CNN
text: President Trump says he doesn't know of a time he's taken more than one Covid-19 test in a day, directly contradicting his press secretary. "I do probably on average a test every two days, three days, and I don't know of any time I've taken two in one day" https://t.co/FSwYkAJsAE

text: As the NBA gears up to resume its season on July 30, the league along with the National Basketball Players Association announced that there were no positive Covid-19 test results from the 346 players that were tested since July 13 https://t.co/OCgoOgxMum
